body:
I believe the following is valid in both Verilog-2005 and SystemVerilog-2017. iverilog currently complains: `error: Cannot assign to array arr1['sd0]. Did you forget a word index?.
```Verilog
module top;
    reg [7:0] arr1 [0:7][0:1];
    reg [7:0] arr2 [0:7][0:1];
    initial arr1[0] = arr2[0];
endmodule
```

